{"tid":1403892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.3 九龍多區警民衝突　警：拘逾 20 人","createTime":"2019-08-04T00:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:47:49.000Z","uid":271434,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d9a42688105261b0ebb17296475177f3113bb3","tid":1403892,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警察公共關係科高級警司余鎧均今早凌晨四時許，交代 8 月 3 日下午至 4 日凌晨在九龍尖沙咀、旺角及黃大仙多區的警民衝突事件，她表示警方拘捕 20 多人，又指在黃大仙的警民衝突中，有示威者換衫後混入居民當中。她又指示威者在尖沙咀警署門外引爆燃燒彈，又用汽油彈攻擊警方。<br />\n<br />\n對於黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍外有人投擲炮仗、玻璃樽和水彈，余鎧均指炮仗是有人在宿舍外燃燒，想投入宿舍前爆開，對於是否有人從宿舍投擲其他物品，她稱警方會不偏不倚跟進。稍後有更詳細報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/8-3-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%AD%A6-%E6%8B%98%E9%80%BE-20-%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9C%89%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8F%9B%E8%A1%AB%E6%B7%B7%E5%85%A5%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-3-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E6%258B%2598%25E9%2580%25BE-20-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258F%259B%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%2F&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=d71e6c95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-3-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E6%258B%2598%25E9%2580%25BE-20-%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258F%259B%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%2F&h=52cf00df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thes